      <introduction>

        <p>
          Now consider a pattern related to <xref ref="fig-five-dots"/>. <!-- See the student page, Growing Pattern of Dots -->
        </p>
        <p>
          Spend at least 5 minutes thinking about the problem on your own.
        </p>
        <p>
          When everyone in your group is ready, share your solutions to <xref ref="act-growing-dots"/> with each other. 
          Try to resolve any differences you have in your understandings. If you and your group members are still uncertain 
          about something after your discussion, write a question or two to ask the full class. 
        </p>
      </introduction>

      <task xml:id="growing-dots-one">
