            <description>An image showing a series of of 5 steps. Each step is a vertical rectangle containing circles. 
            The number of circles increases with each step creating a larger isoceles right triangle after each step. 
            </description>
            
          </image>
        </figure>
      </task>

      <task xml:id="growing-dots-two">
        <p>
          How are these dots related to the dots you counted in the <xref ref="act-dots"/>?
        </p>
      </task>

      <task xml:id="growing-dots-three">
